# P1 Frontend Map — Login/Auth Runtime Impact Review

Status: DRAFT / READING & MAPPING ONLY
Scope: Frontend only
Repository observed: Arkcom5026/alpha-tech-client
Purpose: Understand FE ownership, dependencies, and risk before modifying Login/Auth.

