## 4. FE Risk Matrix

### High Risk

- Changing authStore shape without updating all consumers.
- Adding guard that redirects before bootstrap/refresh completes.
- Allowing URL shopSlug to override logged-in branch.
- Mixing POS branch identity with online branch auto-select.
- Enabling RBAC while token/session stability is still unresolved.

### Medium Risk

- Header reloading branch from selectedBranchId instead of employee.branchId.
- Duplicate navigation between LoginPage and future guard.
- Logout route being placeholder while route exists.
- apiClient refresh succeeds but identity/branch runtime is not rebuilt.

### Low Risk

- Sidebar visual/menu rendering.
- Static route module definitions.
- sidebarMenuConfig switchboard.
- rbacClient if kept dormant.

